### A3 — Brevo Email Deliverability Verification

**What to verify in Render environment variables:**
```
BREVO_API_KEY         → Must be the LIVE key from Brevo (Settings → API Keys → Live key)
BREVO_SENDER_EMAIL    → support@intelligrid.online  (NOT @intelligrid.store)
BREVO_SENDER_NAME     → IntelliGrid
BREVO_LIST_ID         → The ID of your newsletter list in Brevo (Contacts → Lists)
ADMIN_NOTIFY_EMAIL    → support@intelligrid.online
