**DNS Verification (critical for deliverability):**
1. Go to Brevo → **Senders & IPs → Domains**
2. Verify `intelligrid.online` is added and **all 3 DNS records are green** (SPF, DKIM, DMARC)
3. If any are red, add the missing DNS records in your domain registrar

**Test delivery:** Hit the admin endpoint manually:
```bash
curl -X POST https://<render-url>/api/admin/tools/<any-tool-id>/invite \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <admin-clerk-token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"contactEmail": "your-personal@email.com"}'
```
Check if the invite email lands in your inbox (not spam).

